  "response": "As of 2023, if you're looking for the **best camera phone in the range of \u20b915,000 to \u20b918,000**, here are some top recommendations based on performance, camera quality, and features:\n\n---\n\n### **1. Samsung Galaxy M34 5G**\n   - **Key Camera Features**:\n     - 50MP primary camera with OIS (Optical Image Stabilization)\n     - 8MP ultra-wide, 2MP macro\n     - 13MP front camera\n   - **Other Highlights**:\n     - 6.5\" AMOLED display\n     - 6000mAh battery\n     - Exynos 1280 processor\n   - **Why Buy?**: Excellent camera performance with OIS, great display, and long battery life.\n\n---\n\n### **2. Redmi Note 12**\n   - **Key Camera Features**:\n     - 50MP primary camera\n     - 8MP ultra-wide, 2MP macro\n     - 13MP front camera\n   - **Other Highlights**:\n     - 6.67\" AMOLED display\n     - Snapdragon 685 processor\n     - 5000mAh battery with 33W fast charging\n   - **Why Buy?**: Solid camera performance, AMOLED display, and good overall value.\n\n---\n\n### **3. Realme Narzo 60x 5G**\n   - **Key Camera Features**:\n     - 50MP primary camera\n     - 2MP depth sensor\n     - 8MP front camera\n   - **Other Highlights**:\n     - 6.72\" LCD display\n     - Dimensity 6100+ processor\n     - 5000mAh battery with 33W fast charging\n   - **Why Buy?**: Decent camera setup, 5G support, and sleek design.\n\n---\n\n### **4. Poco M6 Pro 5G**\n   - **Key Camera Features**:\n     - 50MP primary camera\n     - 2MP macro\n     - 8MP front camera\n   - **Other Highlights**:\n     - 6.79\" LCD display\n     - Mediatek Dimensity 6100+ processor\n     - 5000mAh battery with 18W charging\n   - **Why Buy?**: Good performance for the price, 5G support, and reliable camera.\n\n---\n\n### **5. Infinix Zero 30 4G**\n   - **Key Camera Features**:\n     - 108MP primary camera\n     - 2MP macro, 2MP depth\n     - 50MP front camera\n   - **Other Highlights**:\n     - 6.78\" AMOLED display\n     - Mediatek Helio G99 processor\n     - 5000mAh battery\n   - **Why Buy?**: Outstanding camera specs for the price, especially the 108MP main sensor and 50MP selfie camera.\n\n---\n\n### **Final Verdict**:\n- **Best Overall**: **Samsung Galaxy M34 5G** (for OIS and AMOLED display)\n- **Best Value for Money**: **Redmi Note 12** (for AMOLED display and solid performance)\n- **Best for Camera**: **Infinix Zero 30 4G** (for 108MP main sensor and 50MP selfie camera)\n\nAlways check for latest deals and availability before purchasing!",
